013package org.apache.juneau.annotation;
014
015import static java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy.*;
016
017import java.lang.annotation.*;
018
019/**
020 * Swagger items annotation.
021 *
022 * <p>
023 * This class is essentially identical to {@link Items} except it's used for defining items of items.
024 *
025 * <p>
026 * Since annotations cannot be nested, we're forced to create a separate annotation for it.
027 * <br>If you want to nest items further, you have to define them free-form using {@link #items()} as free-form JSON.
028 *
029 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
030 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="https://juneau.apache.org/docs/topics/JuneauBeanSwagger2">Swagger</a>
031 *    <li class='extlink'><a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>
032
033 * </ul>
034 */
035@Documented
036@Retention(RUNTIME)
037public @interface SubItems {
038
039   /**
040    * <mk>default</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
041    *
042    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
043    *    <li class='note'>
044    *       The format is a plain-text string.
045    * </ul>
046    *
047    * @return The annotation value.
048    */
049   String[] _default() default {};
050
051    /**
052     * Optional description for the exposed API.
053     *
054     * @return The annotation value.
055     * @since 9.2.0
056     */
057    String[] description() default {};
058
059   /**
060    * <mk>enum</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
061    *
062    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
063    *    <li class='note'>
064    *       The format is a plain-text string.
065    * </ul>
066    *
067    * @return The annotation value.
068    */
069   String[] _enum() default {};
070
071   /**
072    * <mk>$ref</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
073    *
074    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
075    *    <li class='note'>
076    *       The format is a plain-text string.
077    * </ul>
078    *
079    * @return The annotation value.
080    */
081   String $ref() default "";
082
083   /**
084    * Synonym for {@link #collectionFormat()}.
085    *
086    * @return The annotation value.
087    */
088   String cf() default "";
089
090   /**
091    * <mk>collectionFormat</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
092    *
093    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
094    *    <li class='note'>
095    *       The format is a plain-text string.
096    * </ul>
097    *
098    * @return The annotation value.
099    */
100   String collectionFormat() default "";
101
102   /**
103    * Synonym for {@link #_default()}.
104    *
105    * @return The annotation value.
106    */
107   String[] df() default {};
108
109   /**
110    * Synonym for {@link #_enum()}.
111    *
112    * @return The annotation value.
113    */
114   String[] e() default {};
115
116   /**
117    * Synonym for {@link #exclusiveMaximum()}.
118    *
119    * @return The annotation value.
120    */
121   boolean emax() default false;
122
123   /**
124    * Synonym for {@link #exclusiveMinimum()}.
125    *
126    * @return The annotation value.
127    */
128   boolean emin() default false;
129
130   /**
131    * <mk>exclusiveMaximum</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
132    *
133    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
134    *    <li class='note'>
135    *       The format is a plain-text string.
136    * </ul>
137    *
138    * @return The annotation value.
139    */
140   boolean exclusiveMaximum() default false;
141
142   /**
143    * <mk>exclusiveMinimum</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
144    *
145    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
146    *    <li class='note'>
147    *       The format is a plain-text string.
148    * </ul>
149    *
150    * @return The annotation value.
151    */
152   boolean exclusiveMinimum() default false;
153
154   /**
155    * Synonym for {@link #format()}.
156    *
157    * @return The annotation value.
158    */
159   String f() default "";
160
161   /**
162    * <mk>format</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
163    *
164    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
165    *    <li class='note'>
166    *       The format is a plain-text string.
167    * </ul>
168    *
169    * @return The annotation value.
170    */
171   String format() default "";
172
173   /**
174    * <mk>items</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
175    *
176    * <p>
177    * Describes the type of items in the array.
178    *
179    * <p>
180    * This is a <a class="doclink" href="https://juneau.apache.org/docs/topics/JuneauBeanSwagger2">Swagger</a> object.
181    * <br>It must be declared free-form because it's not possible to nest annotations in Java.
182    *
183    * @return The annotation value.
184    */
185   String[] items() default {};
186
187   /**
188    * Synonym for {@link #maximum()}.
189    *
190    * @return The annotation value.
191    */
192   String max() default "";
193
194   /**
195    * Synonym for {@link #maxItems()}.
196    *
197    * @return The annotation value.
198    */
199   long maxi() default -1;
200
201   /**
202    * <mk>maximum</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
203    *
204    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
205    *    <li class='note'>
206    *       The format is a plain-text string.
207    * </ul>
208    *
209    * @return The annotation value.
210    */
211   String maximum() default "";
212
213   /**
214    * <mk>maxItems</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
215    *
216    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
217    *    <li class='note'>
218    *       The format is a plain-text string.
219    * </ul>
220    *
221    * @return The annotation value.
222    */
223   long maxItems() default -1;
224
225   /**
226    * Synonym for {@link #maxLength()}.
227    *
228    * @return The annotation value.
229    */
230   long maxl() default -1;
231
232   /**
233    * <mk>maxLength</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
234    *
235    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
236    *    <li class='note'>
237    *       The format is a plain-text string.
238    * </ul>
239    *
240    * @return The annotation value.
241    */
242   long maxLength() default -1;
243
244   /**
245    * Synonym for {@link #minimum()}.
246    *
247    * @return The annotation value.
248    */
249   String min() default "";
250
251   /**
252    * Synonym for {@link #minItems()}.
253    *
254    * @return The annotation value.
255    */
256   long mini() default -1;
257
258   /**
259    * <mk>minimum</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
260    *
261    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
262    *    <li class='note'>
263    *       The format is a plain-text string.
264    * </ul>
265    *
266    * @return The annotation value.
267    */
268   String minimum() default "";
269
270   /**
271    * <mk>minItems</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
272    *
273    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
274    *    <li class='note'>
275    *       The format is a plain-text string.
276    * </ul>
277    *
278    * @return The annotation value.
279    */
280   long minItems() default -1;
281
282   /**
283    * Synonym for {@link #minLength()}.
284    *
285    * @return The annotation value.
286    */
287   long minl() default -1;
288
289   /**
290    * <mk>minLength</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
291    *
292    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
293    *    <li class='note'>
294    *       The format is a plain-text string.
295    * </ul>
296    *
297    * @return The annotation value.
298    */
299   long minLength() default -1;
300
301   /**
302    * Synonym for {@link #multipleOf()}.
303    *
304    * @return The annotation value.
305    */
306   String mo() default "";
307
308   /**
309    * <mk>multipleOf</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
310    *
311    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
312    *    <li class='note'>
313    *       The format is a plain-text string.
314    * </ul>
315    *
316    * @return The annotation value.
317    */
318   String multipleOf() default "";
319
320   /**
321    * Synonym for {@link #pattern()}.
322    *
323    * @return The annotation value.
324    */
325   String p() default "";
326
327   /**
328    * <mk>pattern</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
329    *
330    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
331    *    <li class='note'>
332    *       The format is a plain-text string.
333    * </ul>
334    *
335    * @return The annotation value.
336    */
337   String pattern() default "";
338
339   /**
340    * Synonym for {@link #type()}.
341    *
342    * @return The annotation value.
343    */
344   String t() default "";
345
346   /**
347    * <mk>type</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
348    *
349    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
350    *    <li class='note'>
351    *       The format is a plain-text string.
352    * </ul>
353    *
354    * @return The annotation value.
355    */
356   String type() default "";
357
358   /**
359    * Synonym for {@link #uniqueItems()}.
360    *
361    * @return The annotation value.
362    */
363   boolean ui() default false;
364
365   /**
366    * <mk>uniqueItems</mk> field of the <a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/specification/v2#itemsObject">Swagger Items Object</a>.
367    *
368    * <h5 class='section'>Notes:</h5><ul>
369    *    <li class='note'>
370    *       The format is a plain-text string.
371    * </ul>
372    *
373    * @return The annotation value.
374    */
375   boolean uniqueItems() default false;
